ing: 1 (15.5 ounce) can white beans, drained and rinsed
1 cup Dannon Oikos Plain Greek Nonfat Yogurt
Salt and cracked pepper to taste
des: "A layered dip with white beans, arugula, and all the flavors of Tuscany."
ins: In a bowl mash beans to break the surface and blend. Add yogurt, tomatoes, arugula, olives, salt and pepper, mix well, let dip stand 20 minutes before serving.
